  <h1>About QuickTalk</h1>
  <p>QuickTalk is a free anonymous random chat platform built for fast, safe, and fun conversations. Meet strangers from around the world via text, voice or HD video — no account required.</p>
  <p>Premium members unlock gender, country and language filters, priority matching, HD video and an ad-free experience.</p>
